title: EU Main Agenda to Determine Russia’s Readiness to Cooperate on Syria
text: The EU’s main goal for the coming weeks will be to determine Russia’s readiness to cooperate on ending the Syrian civil war, including forming a new government and fighting the Islamic State, German Foreign Minister Frank-Walter Steinmeier said Monday. ...
